<plot>Zen &amp; the Asteroid is a Taoist, Sci-Fi Comedy for all ages. It's about Spaceships and Secret Councils, Mad Doctors and Attractive Androids, Zen Koan Questions and a big Asteroid headed towards Earth. The year is 2073. When the eternal spirit of Zen gets bored and decides to have some fun with an asteroid, Earth's very existence is at stake. The Council gathers on the Martian moon-base Phobos and decides to stop Zen and save the Earth by sending the Investigators--an assorted group of Mars' most talented Bounty Hunters.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?670037</url></doc>
